data.title: Bazooka 270 Men's Complete Set
data.text:
270

DRIVER GRAPHITE SHAFT

Oversize high-MOI 460CC driver promotes increased forgiveness on off-center hits for longer, straighter tee shots. Headcover included.

FAIRWAY WOODS #3 GRAPHITE SHAFT

Oversize low-profile stainless steel fairway wood is designed with a low CG to get the ball easily into the air. Headcover included.

HYBRIDS #4 STEEL SHAFT

Easy-to-hit hybrid features a deep CG and low profile design for maximum carry and soft landing. Headcover included.

IRONS #5 - SW STEEL SHAFT

Oversized, stainless steel irons feature and undercut cavity for more forgiveness and a larger sweet spot for higher, accurate shots.

PUTTERS

High-MOI heel-toe weighted putter with an easy-to-use alignment aid delivers more accurate putts.

DUAL STRAP STAND BAG

Premium lightweight stand bag with six-way divider top, dual carry strap and four zippered pockets. Rain hood included.

SPECS

Available in men's right hand. Graphite shaft flex is R/S. Steel hybrid & iron (5-SW) shaft flex is R/S. Headcovers are included with woods and hybrid.
